project_descr: Tisza community-led demonstration project for sustainable development and integrated land and water management

outputs.output_descr: The Tisza community-led demonstration project for sustainable development and integrated land and water management is an integral part of the GEF- Mid-Size Project "Establishment of Mechanisms for Integrated Land and Water Management in the Tisza River Basin". This pilot and demonstration component will aim at developing, implementation and evaluation of a transboundary community-led projects that promote sustainable development through integrated land and water management practices at the community level.
